         <text>Flow has been migrated to BIC. Please inform Process Steward: Mariana Campos Guilcrits &lt;mariana.campos.guilcrits@intel.com&gt;, and BPM Champion: Marie Joseph &lt;marie.joseph@intel.com&gt; of any changes that occur within the flow.</text>
